snippet.title: Super Mario Bros Extreme Adventure | DEMO Relase Trailer
snippet.description:
This MOD is not affiliated with Nintendo or Team Newer, 
for what we have used their material: we do not intend to earn money and fame. 
Mario, Luigi and all the characters inside
of the game are for Copyright ©Nintendo.
but we only hope you enjoy playing that MOD.
For any doubts or bugs, contact us via our social networks, good gameplay ;).
We thank enormously the help received from the server Discord and website of Horizion Miraheze.
We not endorse Piracy
--------------------------------------------------------------------
SMB: Extreme Adventure | The DEMO Relase Trailer

DOWNLOAD NOW!: 
https://github.com/TeamAlternative2023/SMBEA/releases

No Copyright Music by Nintendo
Music: Toad's Factory
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZEgzDR6_W-I&t=0s
Toad's Factory - Mario Kart Wii
Author: Asuka Ota & Ryo Nagamatsu
  
We thank enormously Synel in the Horizon Discord server for a Custom Muncher Sprite and the Newer Team for NewerSMBW
